item.title: www.businesswire.com
item.description: Business Wire disseminates press releases to various disclosure targets, e.g news media (e.g. NYT, WSJ), financial markets, financial databases, terminals, etc. Looks like a good source of information that then gets reported by news outlets with additional context. Biased to be positive though as it is coming from the company in question. Press release distribution, EDGAR filing, XBRL, regulatory filings | Business Wire. www.businesswire.com .

item.title: dl.acm.org
item.description: ACM’s Digital Library contains lots of current research, albeit some behind a paywall. To easily import ACM DL’s BibTeX citations, use the (author|title|year|isbn|url|booktitle|keywords) = \{(.*)\},? regex and do a \t$1="$2"\n list on https://regexr.com/ .
